129
00:06:00,011 --> 00:06:01,665
To je dugo vreme za dete.

130
00:06:06,148 --> 00:06:07,584
U redu.

131
00:06:07,628 --> 00:06:08,629
Da.

132
00:06:09,934 --> 00:06:11,327
Kako je Džesi?

133
00:06:11,371 --> 00:06:13,285
On je dobro.

134
00:06:13,329 --> 00:06:17,507
Pametan je i tako je čudan.

135
00:06:17,551 --> 00:06:21,381
Stariji je i smešan je
i ne znam, on je...

136
00:06:21,424 --> 00:06:24,209
On je... on je jedna cela mala ličnost.

137
00:06:25,167 --> 00:06:28,257
I Pol se preselio u Okland.

138
00:06:28,997 --> 00:06:30,346
- Je li?

139
00:06:30,390 --> 00:06:31,739
- Da.

140
00:06:31,782 --> 00:06:33,175
- Stvarno?

141
00:06:34,219 --> 00:06:35,482
- Da, to je u redu.

142
00:06:35,525 --> 00:06:37,397
Ja... to je... mislim tako.

143
00:06:37,440 --> 00:06:39,964
Džesi se nosi sa tom dobro do sada,

144
00:06:40,008 --> 00:06:41,923
ali Pol ne.

145
00:06:41,966 --> 00:06:43,185
- On je...

146
00:06:43,228 --> 00:06:45,927
Mislim, on... Ja samo...

147
00:06:45,970 --> 00:06:47,189
On je dobro.

148
00:06:47,232 --> 00:06:49,074
Ja samo moram da odem gore
i pomognem malo.

149
00:06:49,099 --> 00:06:50,410
Pomognem mu da se sredi.

150
00:06:51,149 --> 00:06:52,324
- Oh, da?

151
00:06:53,064 --> 00:06:54,457
- Da.

152
