- Reci zdravo.

162
00:08:19,934 --> 00:08:21,718
"Zdravo, kako si?"

163
00:08:21,762 --> 00:08:22,980
- Kako si?

164
00:08:23,024 --> 00:08:24,373
Dobro sam. Kako si ti?

165
00:08:25,374 --> 00:08:26,375
- Dobro sam.

166
00:08:28,420 --> 00:08:30,553
Da li ćeš da pitaš ujka Džonija da uđe?

167
00:08:30,597 --> 00:08:32,555
- Treba da me pitaš da uđem.

168
00:08:32,599 --> 00:08:33,600
Da li želiš da uđeš?

169
00:08:33,643 --> 00:08:34,949
- Hvala.
- U redu.

170
00:08:36,037 --> 00:08:37,232
- Dobiću zagrljaj?

171
00:08:42,826 --> 00:08:43,914
- Zdravo.
- Zdravo.

172
00:08:53,576 --> 00:08:57,101
- Imamo njene haljine,

173
00:08:57,145 --> 00:08:59,408
sve moje domaće stvari.

174
00:09:00,801 --> 00:09:03,586
- Kul.

175
00:09:03,630 --> 00:09:05,675
- Mama kaže da ćeš spavati ovde noćas

176
